OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FThousands of people are without water
OL,7,Fin the Conwy Valley after a burst
OL,8,Fwater main at a treatment works near
OL,9,FDolgarrog.
OL,11,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water had said it was
OL,12,Fexpected that supplies would be
OL,13,Frestored by the end of the day on
OL,14,FThursday, but have now confirmed some
OL,15,Fpeople in the area could be without
OL,16,Fsupply for 48 hours.
OL,18,FWelsh Water have confirmed around
OL,19,F8,000 households have currently lost
OL,20,Fsupply, with a further 33,000 at risk
OL,21,Funtil the repair is completed.
