OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FThe burst main is at the Bryn Cowlyd
OL,7,FWater Treatment Works and is impacting
OL,8,Fproperties in Conwy, Colwyn Bay,
OL,9,FLlanrwst, Llandudno, Dolgarrog and
OL,10,Fsurrounding areas.
OL,12,FThe water company said repair work was
OL,13,Ftaking longer than planned and is
OL,14,Fproving to be "exceptionally
OL,15,Fdifficult" due to the burst main being
OL,16,Flocated two and a half meters under
OL,17,Fthe river bed of Afon Ddu.
