OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FThe network includes service
OL,7,Freservoirs that store water and mains
OL,8,Fthat deliver the water to the
OL,9,Fcustomers. As a result Welsh Water
OL,10,Fsays it will take time for the system
OL,11,Fto re-fill to a sufficient level to
OL,12,Frestore the supply to customers.
OL,14,FBottled water is being delivered to
OL,15,Fparticularly vulnerable people, which
OL,16,Fequates to around 5,000 people.
