OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FThey say that they are tankering water
OL,7,Finto the network to maintain supplies
OL,8,Fto local hospitals. Six schools in
OL,9,FConwy have closed as a result of the
OL,10,Fburst main, with businesses impacted
OL,11,Falso closed.
OL,13,FA coffer dam structure has been
OL,14,Fcreated to redirect the river to allow
OL,15,Fspecialist crews to access the damaged
OL,16,Fwater main.
