OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FA Welsh Water spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Frepair to the burst water main at our
OL,8,FBryn Cowlyd Water Treatment Works,
OL,9,FDolgarrog is taking longer than was
OL,10,Fplanned.
OL,12,F"The burst water main is two and half
OL,13,Fmetres beneath the riverbed and the
OL,14,Fvolume of water in the river is making
OL,15,Fthe repair exceptionally difficult."
