OL,3,CThousands of homes could be without
OL,4,Cwater for days due to burst water main
OL,6,FThe water company said that the
OL,7,Fprocess to repair the main couldn't be
OL,8,Frushed as it could cause ongoing
OL,9,Fissues with water pressure,
OL,10,Fdiscolouration of water or further
OL,11,Fbursts.
OL,13,F"We are prioritising delivering
OL,14,Fbottled water to vulnerable customers
OL,15,Fon our Priority Services Register.
OL,16,FThis involves supporting 5,000
OL,17,Fvulnerable customers in the affected
OL,18,Fareas.
