OL,6,F"We intend to have bottled water
OL,7,Fstations in place tomorrow, but as
OL,8,Fthere is currently a shortage in the
OL,9,Fbulk supplies of bottled water across
OL,10,Fthe UK and we are sourcing bottled
OL,11,Fwater from as far as Scotland. We're
OL,12,Fusing current supplies to prioritise
OL,13,Four vulnerable customers.
OL,15,F"Compensation arrangements will be put
OL,16,Fin place to those customers who have
OL,17,Flost their supplies together with
OL,18,Fadditional arrangements for business
OL,19,Fcustomers.
